trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView" /> entity that owns the cell style that was changed.
trans-unit.target: Especifica a entidade <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView" /> que possui o estilo de célula que foi alterado.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyleContentChangedEventArgs> to indicate which part of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> owns the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyle> that changed.
trans-unit.target: Essa enumeração é usada por <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyleContentChangedEventArgs> para indicar qual parte do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> possui o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellStyle> que foram alteradas.

trans-unit.source: One or more values of the object returned by the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.AlternatingRowsDefaultCellStyle" /> property changed.
trans-unit.target: Um ou mais valores do objeto retornado pela propriedade <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.AlternatingRowsDefaultCellStyle" /> foi alterado.
